Diego Melgar
04/2013

This program computes displacement response spectra from acceleration
or displacement (GPS) data. It solves the ODE for a single degree
of freedom harmonic oscillator using finite differences. If you use
this code please reference:

Melgar, D., Y. Bock, D. Sanchez, and B.W. Crowell (2013), On robust and 
reliable automated baseline corrections for strong motion seismology, 
J. Geophys. Res., 118, doi: 10.1002/jgrb.50135
